<div class="authi">
<img class="authicn vm" id="authicon71086219" src="static/image/common/online_member.gif" />
<em id="authorposton71086219">发表于 2013-12-14 12:09</em>
<span class="pipe">|</span>
<a href="http://bbs.rednet.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=42575191&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=4020827" rel="nofollow">只看该作者</a>
